{"tid":724967,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【神秘聲波】《紐時》：京滬駐華使館「受襲」 至少11人返美作檢查","createTime":"2018-07-01T11:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T11:22:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"026fec8be9b6ed3f993d5e74bb0962c77a057364","tid":724967,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180701/large/1530441696_319c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180701%2Flarge%2F1530441696_319c.jpg&h=b4c5a384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國駐中國外交人員疑遭音波攻擊範圍擴大。《紐約時報》昨日報道，最近美國駐上海領事館、北京大使館都傳出疑遭攻擊案例，加上4月最先傳出受害的廣州領事館，美國前後已撤回至少11名外館人員及眷屬回美做進一步檢查。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院昨日發表書面聲明證實，的確有「幾名領事館人員及家屬」被送回美國做進一步檢查，但強調有些可能跟音波攻擊無關。美國國務院已派遣資深官員赴中調查，檢視駐外人員的「怪病」，但迄今仍不知道成因為何。<br />\n<br />\n今年4月傳出美國駐廣州領事館人員，在居住的高級社區大樓聽到怪聲或感受到異常壓力，最先撤離的1名職員確診受到輕度腦傷。不願具名的美國官員向《紐時》透露，美國駐廣州領事館4月至今已撤離至少8人，最近上海領事館也撤離1名職員，北京大使館撤離2人，但不清楚上海和北京撤離人員受傷原因是否跟廣州一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180701/58387716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180701%2F58387716&d=R2cxRVh4lUvNNuaWy%2FjklsmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=5b65ca6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180701%2F58387716&h=2557d71d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180701/58387716</a>"},{"pid":"0dbef61eb445c434f9e458f933fd3054b8ab7d58","tid":724967,"uid":51840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:07:18.000Z","msg":"質與量的反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2e87f13b336c9d995fce791228a7bae1f9ba56","tid":724967,"uid":101919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:19:25.000Z","msg":"現代義和團？想黎多次八國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1cf32ebce0d0763d34f038be957ddd2ebe5d4f","tid":724967,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:22:21.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢仲特登走去搞鳩美國人"}]}